generateKeyPair

  • generateKeyPair(): JWKeyPair
    • Defined in lib-client/asmail/keyring/common.ts:56

    Returns JWKeyPair

    an object with two fields: skey & pkey, holding JWK form of secret and public keys respectively. These are to be used with NaCl's box (Curve+XSalsa+Poly encryption). Key ids are the same in this intimate pair.

generateSymmetricKey

  • generateSymmetricKey(): JsonKey
    • Defined in lib-client/asmail/keyring/common.ts:78

    We have this function for future use by a keyring, that takes symmetric key. This keyring, is specifically tailored to handle short-lived public keys. Therefore, this function is not used at the moment.

    Returns JsonKey

    a JWK form of a key for NaCl's secret box (XSalsa+Poly encryption).
